# Google Cloud OAuth 2.0 access token (cloud-platform scope). Referenced from the
# Authorization header; credproxy swaps the placeholder for the real token at
# egress to sqladmin.googleapis.com, so it never enters the agent sandbox.
GOOGLE_CLOUD_ACCESS_TOKEN
# Google Cloud project ID, sent as the x-goog-user-project header for quota and
# billing routing.
GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT
